>
> ***Magic Resistance.*** The elemental has advantage on saving throws versus spells and other magical effects. 
>
> ### Actions
> ***Touch.*** *Melee Weapon Attack:* +4 to hit, reach 5 ft., one target. *Hit:* 6 (1d8 + 2) force damage. If the target is a creature, it must succeed on a DC 11 Strength saving throw or be knocked prone.
>
